ZH: 他今天去医院就诊。
EN: He went to the hospital for a check-up today.

ZH: 我需要去看医生就诊。
EN: I need to see a doctor for a consultation.

ZH: 请问您是来就诊的吗？
EN: May I ask if you are here for an appointment?

ZH: 我需要预约才能就诊吗？
EN: Do I need an appointment to see a doctor?

ZH: 请问你需要就诊哪一位医生？
EN: Which doctor would you like to see for your appointment?

ZH: 明天我要去医院就诊。
EN: I have an appointment at the hospital tomorrow for a check-up.

ZH: 我们需要等一下才能就诊。
EN: We need to wait a little before we can see the doctor.

ZH: 这个诊所提供急诊和普通就诊服务。
EN: This clinic offers both urgent care and regular check-ups.

ZH: 他一直在等待就诊。
EN: He has been waiting to see the doctor.

ZH: 我们需要先填写一些表格才能就诊。
EN: We need to fill out some forms before we can see the doctor.

ZH: 就诊时间从早上九点到下午五点。
EN: Consultation hours are from 9am to 5pm.

ZH: 我们的医生已经忙于就诊。
EN: Our doctor is busy with consultations.

ZH: 请在前台登记后再就诊。
EN: Please register at the front desk before seeing the doctor.

ZH: 我会提前打电话预约就诊。
EN: I will call ahead to make an appointment for the consultation.

ZH: 他预计需要多次就诊才能康复。
EN: He is expected to need multiple consultations to recover.

ZH: 医院对急诊和普通就诊进行了分开。
EN: The hospital has separate areas for urgent care and regular check-ups.

ZH: 我们需要去就诊室等候。
EN: We need to go to the consultation room to wait.

ZH: 医生建议我尽快就诊。
EN: The doctor advised me to seek consultation as soon as possible.

ZH: 我需要去医院就诊做个体检。
EN: I need to go to the hospital for a check-up and physical examination.

ZH: 昨天他去了医院就诊。
EN: He went to the hospital for a consultation yesterday.
